I get to go to work
with my best friend...

15:42.593 --> 15:44.726
...my best friends

15:44.769 --> 15:46.771
every day.

15:48.773 --> 15:50.688
And I'm not ready...

15:50.732 --> 15:53.517
I'm not ready to let that go.

15:54.779 --> 15:56.738
Well, neither am I.

15:56.781 --> 15:58.087
Felix, listen,

15:58.131 --> 15:59.523
if we get this money,

15:59.567 --> 16:01.917
we could make a donation,
and then we're good.

