16:15.800 --> 16:18.020
Which could work.
That could work.

16:19.369 --> 16:20.762
Yeah?

16:20.805 --> 16:22.677
Yeah.

16:23.678 --> 16:25.680
[exhales]Okay.

16:26.811 --> 16:28.552
So, Murphy told me

16:28.596 --> 16:30.554
