17:13.510 --> 17:15.208
No, he wasn't.
He said that?

17:15.251 --> 17:17.732
Yeah. He said he... he said
he was gonna... he had to do

17:17.775 --> 17:19.777
a report or...
or he said he...

17:19.821 --> 17:23.085
he said you needed his help
with something. Or...

17:23.129 --> 17:25.087
