25:30.616 --> 25:35.359
♪ Please be true

25:35.403 --> 25:40.843
♪ In other words

25:40.887 --> 25:45.848
♪ I love

25:45.892 --> 25:49.199
♪ You.

25:55.641 --> 25:58.557
That was incredible.

26:00.428 --> 26:02.648
It was.

26:06.477 --> 26:10.699
