26:10.743 --> 26:11.744
What?

26:13.702 --> 26:16.836
I know what you did.

26:16.879 --> 26:19.665
I know it was you.

26:22.668 --> 26:25.888
Murphy, what are you...
talking about?

26:32.286 --> 26:35.115
You don't have
