26:53.568 --> 26:54.787
'Cause they're just
trying to manipulate...

26:54.830 --> 26:56.745
Stop.

26:58.573 --> 27:00.575
Stop.

27:01.968 --> 27:04.057
Those matches I found
in your car...

27:04.100 --> 27:05.841
[shudders, sighs]

27:05.885 --> 27:08.191
