29:27.722 --> 29:30.594
Oh, my God. Oh, my God. And then he got into trouble.

29:30.638 --> 29:32.466
Just keep your mouth
shut, all right?

29:32.509 --> 29:34.163
Worst case, we'll be out
in a couple months.

29:34.207 --> 29:35.599
A couple months?

29:35.643 --> 29:36.687
SARAH:
Wesley,

29:36.731 --> 29:38.994
you're up.

29:50.789 --> 29:52.791
[exhales]

30:02.626 --> 30:05.586
Well, this is not ideal, huh?

30:05.629 --> 30:08.632
Look, I don't want any trouble,
