30:08.676 --> 30:10.591
What's your name?

30:10.634 --> 30:12.593
Tyson Parker.

30:12.636 --> 30:14.638
What are you in for?

30:14.682 --> 30:16.989
Possession.

30:17.990 --> 30:19.165
[sighs]

30:19.208 --> 30:22.516
