30:43.842 --> 30:45.582
Yeah.

30:45.626 --> 30:47.541
Right.

30:47.584 --> 30:49.499
Good.

30:49.543 --> 30:52.502
Sit tight,
Tyson Parker.

30:52.546 --> 30:54.548
But, two months later,

30:54.591 --> 30:55.897
