31:29.757 --> 31:31.237
I am sorry. I can't.

31:31.280 --> 31:34.022
Okay, then I'll tell him
the real reason I got out.

31:34.066 --> 31:36.633
I'll tell him
everything about you.

31:38.679 --> 31:40.072
