33:12.903 --> 33:14.731
Somebody help!

33:19.171 --> 33:21.173
[panting]

33:21.216 --> 33:23.218
[grunts]

33:32.749 --> 33:35.796
[muffled groan]
Ow. W-Wait.

33:35.839 --> 33:38.407
Wait. Wait! Wait![shushing]

33:38.451 --> 33:40.322
Wait, Dean! No! Please!

33:40.366 --> 33:42.803
Somebody help! Somebody help!

33:47.590 --> 33:50.550
Murphy.

33:50.593 --> 33:52.552
[sighs]

33:52.595 --> 33:55.772
Just please say something.

33:55.816 --> 33:57.600
[exhales]

33:59.428 --> 34:02.692
Never tell anyone
what you just told me.

34:04.999 --> 34:06.740
So you understand?

34:09.525 --> 34:11.701
You did it for Chloe.

34:13.747 --> 34:17.185
Everything I do is for Chloe.

34:17.229 --> 34:20.667
I know.
[sighs]

34:20.710 --> 34:23.452
[breathing deeply]

34:32.896 --> 34:34.898
It's okay.

34:46.867 --> 34:48.869
♪

35:02.883 --> 35:05.451
[whispers]:
Stop recording.

35:05.494 --> 35:07.540
AUTOMATED VOICE:
Stopping recording.

35:10.847 --> 35:13.763
Everything okay in there?

35:13.807 --> 35:16.070
MURPHY:
Yeah, just a second.

35:20.814 --> 35:22.816
[whimpers]

35:35.611 --> 35:37.135
[grunts softly]

35:50.365 --> 35:52.367
[gasps, screams]Where are you going?

35:52.411 --> 35:53.716
Let's talk about this.No!

35:53.760 --> 35:54.804
Help! Help!Stop screaming.

36:04.074 --> 36:05.815
Delete all recordings.

36:05.859 --> 36:08.557
AUTOMATED VOICE:
Deleting recordings.

36:12.605 --> 36:16.609
This can't get out,
you know that.

36:16.652 --> 36:18.698
This... [scoffs]

36:18.741 --> 36:20.700
It can't.

36:23.833 --> 36:26.575
I know that you care about me.

36:26.619 --> 36:29.535
We just made love.

36:29.578 --> 36:31.885
That's the thing.

36:31.928 --> 36:34.757
Sex means nothing to me.

36:34.801 --> 36:37.412
I just use it
to get what I want.

36:37.456 --> 36:39.066
And I did.

36:39.109 --> 36:42.243
How can you
do that to me?

36:42.287 --> 36:43.549
Yeah. [scoffs]

36:43.592 --> 36:45.507
You're the victim here.

36:45.551 --> 36:46.900
Think about Chloe.

36:46.943 --> 36:48.989
The fact that I have a
family; I have a life.

36:49.032 --> 36:51.121
You should have thought about
that before you murdered a kid.

36:51.165 --> 36:53.428
He had a family.

36:53.472 --> 36:55.213
He had a life.

36:55.256 --> 36:56.910
And you took that away from him.

36:56.953 --> 36:58.259
He brought it on himself.

36:58.303 --> 36:59.608
Okay, it's his fault.

36:59.652 --> 37:00.653
It's not just mine.

37:00.696 --> 37:02.220
He threatened me.

37:02.263 --> 37:04.787
And now I'm threatening you.

37:04.831 --> 37:06.702
Are you gonna kill me, too?

37:06.746 --> 37:08.574
Just keep
silencing everybody?

37:08.617 --> 37:10.532
What makes you think your life
is so important?

37:10.576 --> 37:12.882
There's nothing special
about you.

37:14.667 --> 37:16.582
Nothing.

37:18.975 --> 37:21.282
Wait.

37:21.326 --> 37:24.154
Murphy, the car is moving.I don't care.

37:24.198 --> 37:25.678
Stop![tires squeal]

37:25.721 --> 37:27.506
[Murphy grunts]

37:27.549 --> 37:28.550
I'm sorry.

37:28.594 --> 37:30.335
Hey. Hey, I'm sorry.

37:30.378 --> 37:31.379
I'm sorry.

37:31.423 --> 37:32.685
Murphy, I'm-I'm sorry.

37:32.728 --> 37:34.687
[groans]
Please. Ju...

37:34.730 --> 37:36.732
[panting, stammering]

37:40.258 --> 37:41.781
[Murphy grunting]Stop!

37:48.440 --> 37:50.790
Don't make me do this.

37:50.833 --> 37:53.488
What am I making you do?
What am I making you do?

37:53.532 --> 37:55.621
What am I making you do?!

37:55.664 --> 37:58.319
[both grunting]

38:02.410 --> 38:04.107
[grunting continues]

38:04.151 --> 38:05.718
[horn honking]

38:05.761 --> 38:07.981
[tires squealing]

38:18.687 --> 38:20.689
♪

38:22.691 --> 38:24.693
♪

38:26.260 --> 38:27.609
I like it.

38:27.653 --> 38:28.654
Who is this?

38:28.697 --> 38:30.395
Labi Siffre.

38:30.438 --> 38:31.657
Who?

38:31.700 --> 38:32.832
Labi Siffre.

38:32.875 --> 38:35.008
Not a lot of people know
who he is,

38:35.051 --> 38:38.925
but he influenced,
like, everybody.

38:38.968 --> 38:41.275
This is the kind of guy that
I want to be when I grow up.

38:41.319 --> 38:43.538
You want to influence everybody?

38:43.582 --> 38:47.237
I just kind of want to,
like, have an impact.

38:47.281 --> 38:48.761
More so.

38:48.804 --> 38:50.980
You have an impact on me.

38:51.024 --> 38:53.461
Mm. I guess that'll
do... for now.

38:53.505 --> 38:54.984
Oh, for now?

38:55.028 --> 38:56.812
Hey, listen.

38:56.856 --> 38:59.598
All I'm saying is you don't
know where I'm going.

38:59.641 --> 39:01.600
♪ See me flame

39:01.643 --> 39:04.472
No one knows where
they're going.

39:04.516 --> 39:05.691
♪ Sing a song

39:05.734 --> 39:07.693
I love you, Murph.

39:07.736 --> 39:09.564
I love you, too, kid.

39:09.608 --> 39:13.133
♪ Oh, I'm so...

39:13.176 --> 39:14.830
♪ Glad you came

39:14.874 --> 39:17.093
♪ [monitor beeping]

39:17.137 --> 39:19.139
It's Murphy.

39:21.620 --> 39:24.797
Now you know what it's
like to feel helpless.

39:24.840 --> 39:26.842
[chuckles]

39:29.715 --> 39:33.240
By the way, your confession
that I recorded saved

39:33.283 --> 39:36.765
to the cloud, so...

39:36.809 --> 39:38.419
You're done.

39:38.463 --> 39:41.291
You know, I thought about...

39:41.335 --> 39:43.685
all the things I would say
to Tyson's killer

39:43.729 --> 39:48.560
if I ever got this chance...
but...

39:48.603 --> 39:50.866
now that I'm actually here...

39:50.910 --> 39:53.652
[sniffles]

39:53.695 --> 39:57.046
I don't want to tell you
what a bad person you are.

39:57.090 --> 39:59.484
♪ You are

39:59.527 --> 40:01.486
♪ I'm still falling

40:01.529 --> 40:03.357
I want to talk about

40:03.401 --> 40:06.795
what a good person he was.

40:06.839 --> 40:10.233
So you're gonna lie there
and listen

40:10.277 --> 40:13.019
to every single thing
I can remember about him.

40:13.062 --> 40:17.240
Every single thing
I couldn't even think about,

40:17.284 --> 40:21.723
[sniffles]
because I was so obsessed...

40:21.767 --> 40:23.595
with finding you.

40:23.638 --> 40:25.597
♪

40:25.640 --> 40:28.338
[sighs]

40:28.382 --> 40:30.340
[sniffles]

40:30.384 --> 40:32.473
Hi, Murphy.

40:32.517 --> 40:35.345
It's Nia.

40:35.389 --> 40:37.043
Oh.

40:37.086 --> 40:38.740
Hello.

40:38.784 --> 40:40.699
Look like your work friends
stole my money.

40:40.742 --> 40:41.830
What?

40:41.874 --> 40:43.876
Your coworkers.

40:45.965 --> 40:47.967
Oh, my God.

40:48.010 --> 40:50.099
Jess.

40:50.143 --> 40:51.666
Oh, my God.

40:51.710 --> 40:54.234
Um...

40:54.277 --> 40:56.671
They have nothing to do
with this.

40:56.715 --> 41:00.327
I will find a way to pay
you back. I'm sorry, but...

41:00.370 --> 41:02.460
Oh, I don't want you
to pay it back.

41:02.503 --> 41:04.374
It's a gift.

41:05.985 --> 41:07.508
W-What do you mean?

41:07.552 --> 41:09.031
Actually, it's not a gift.

41:09.075 --> 41:11.381
It's an investment.

41:11.425 --> 41:14.123
See, when your boyfriend ran
off, I lost one of my fronts.

41:14.167 --> 41:17.126
And I've been in need of
a replacement, and then poof.

41:17.170 --> 41:19.607
God brought me Guiding Hope.

41:19.651 --> 41:22.175
You want us to launder
money for you?

41:22.218 --> 41:23.611
I don't-- That's
not a good idea.

41:23.655 --> 41:25.178
It's a win-win.

41:25.221 --> 41:26.962
You keep your company,
I keep mine.

41:27.006 --> 41:28.747
I've very lucrative.

41:28.790 --> 41:30.226
What do you say?

41:30.270 --> 41:34.187
Um, thank you,
that's a-a nice offer, but...

41:34.230 --> 41:37.190
unfortunately, there's no way
Felix or Jess would...

41:37.233 --> 41:39.888
No, they're in; they were in
when they stole my money.

41:39.932 --> 41:42.935
Unless you're planning
on paying me back right now,

41:42.978 --> 41:45.677
this negotiation is over.

41:45.720 --> 41:47.722
[gasps]

41:51.509 --> 41:53.511
I'll see you soon, Murphy.

41:56.688 --> 41:58.211
What is this?

41:58.254 --> 41:59.560
What is it?

41:59.604 --> 42:01.170
What does this open?

42:01.214 --> 42:03.390
What does this do?

42:03.433 --> 42:04.696
Hello?

